<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.6.7">
<l>koṇṭaravat tiraiyulavu kuraikaṭalmēl kulavaraipōl</l>
<l>paṇṭaravi ṉaṇaikkiṭantu pāraḷanta paṇpāḷā</l>
<l>vaṇṭamarum vaḷarppoḻilcūḻ vayalāli maintāveṉ</l>
<l>kaṇṭuyilnī koṇṭāykkeṉ kaṉavaḷaiyuṅ kaṭavēṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Noble who measured the earth, having laid long ago on a serpent bed</l>
<l>Like a mountain range in the vast sea which stirs with roaring waves,</l>
<l>[My] man of Āli where paddy fields are surrounded by tall groves</l>
<l rend="indent">where bees settle,</l>
<l>To you who [already] took my sleep [from my] eyes, must I also [surrender]</l>
<l rend="indent">my golden bangles?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
